     H            Y.
     F** FBCR83 ******************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : CHECK FBCWP83(SALES-UP.CSV)                    *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 03/30/2016                                     *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                       *
     F*  FUNCTION   : READ FBCWP83(CSV) AND VALIDATE FIELDS          *
     F*             : IF ERROR, CREATE ERROR REPORT                  *
     *  ATTENTION  : COMPILE WITH OPTION - ALLOW NULL VALUES *YES
     F*             : -------------------------------                *
JW1  F*  JW         2019.11.08 ACCEPT PAST DATE FOR EFFECTIVE DATE   *
JW2  F*  JW         2023.06.19 FIX MHIN BUG                          *
JW3  F*  JW         2023.12.01 FIX CUST/DELV 4 DIGIT NUMBER ISSUE    *
     F****************************************************************
     FFBCWP83 IF  E                    DISK
     FFAAPL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFBCPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFBCWP84 O   E           K        DISK
     FQPRINT  O   F     132     OF     PRINTER
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    CSV        80  1
     E                    FLD        20  1
     E**                  MV1        20  1
     E**                  MV2        20  1
     E                    MSG     1  13 80
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
      *
     I              '0123456789 '         C         WKCKSU
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 K@SHN
     I                                        1   5 K@SHN1
     I                                        6  10 K@SHN2
     I                                       11  12 K@SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 @MHIN
     I                                        1   5 @MHIN1
     I                                        6  10 @MHIN2
     I                                       11  15 @MHIN3
     I                                       16  20 @MHIN4
     I                                       11  12 @MHIN5
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 W@FLD6
     I                                        1   65W@NUM6
     ID10@DT      DS
     I                                        1   4 D10@YY
     I                                        6   7 D10@MM
     I                                        9  10 D10@DD
     ID8@DT       DS
     I                                        1   4 D8@YY
     I                                        5   6 D8@MM
     I                                        7   8 D8@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@EFDT
     I                                        1   40@TKYY
     I                                        5   60@TKMM
     I                                        7   80@TKDD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
      * Initial Process
     C                     EXSR @INIT
      * Validate U/P Data
     C                     EXSR @CHK1
      * Print Footer
     C           NM@CNT    ADD  ER@CNT    TTL#
      *
     C           SEQ       IFEQ 0
      * If No Error
     C                     MOVE *OFF      #STS
     C                     MOVE MSG,6     FLD37  37
     C                     MOVELWR@CNT    FLD37
     C                     MOVE MSG,6     FLD42  52
     C                     MOVELDAT#      FLD42
     C                     MOVELMSG,6     #MSG1
     C                     MOVE FLD42     #MSG1
     C                     MOVE FLD37     #MSG1
     C                     ELSE
      * If Error
     C                     MOVE *ON       #STS
     C                     EXCPTFOT1
     C                     MOVE MSG,7     FLD36  36
     C                     MOVELOK@CNT    FLD36
     C                     MOVE MSG,7     FLD46  46
     C                     MOVELWR@CNT    FLD46
     C                     MOVE MSG,7     FLD61  61
     C                     MOVELER@CNT    FLD61
     C                     MOVELMSG,7     #MSG2
     C                     MOVE FLD61     #MSG2
     C                     MOVE FLD46     #MSG2
     C                     MOVE FLD36     #MSG2
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      ******************************************************
      *          Validate U/P Data
      ******************************************************
     C           @CHK1     BEGSR
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN80
      *
     C           *IN80     DOUEQ*ON
     C                     READ FBCWP83                  80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     ADD  1         LIN#
     C                     EXSR @GET
      * If Header, Skip
     C           #HDFLG    IFEQ *ON
     C                     GOTO @SKIP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         DAT#
     C                     MOVE *OFF      #ERFLG  1
      * A:Check CUSTOMER#---------------------------
     C           #TOKU     CHAINFGBPL01              98
      *     Print Err Report: ERROR - CUSTOMER CODE IS NOT IN MASTER FILE!
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *ON
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,8     XMSG   35
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      * B:Check DELIVERY#---------------------------
     C           #NONY     CHAINFGBPL01              98
      *     Print Err Report: ERROR - DELIVERY CODE IS NOT IN MASTER FILE!
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *ON
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,9     XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      * C:Check Factory Code------------------------
      * D:Check Dock CODE---------------------------
      * E:Check Part 1-----------------------------------
      *      (*) CHAIN FAAPP02(B7) COMMON PART M/F
     C                     MOVE *OFF      EXIST1  1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    K@SHN
     C                     MOVEL#PART2    @MHIN
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN98
     C           K#PART    SETLLFAAPL05
     C           *IN98     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           K#PART    READEFAAPL05                  98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE *ON       EXIST1
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      * Check Part 2-----------------------------------
      *      (*) CHAIN FCEPP01(A2) PRODUCTION M
     C                     MOVE *OFF      EXIST2  1
     C                     MOVEL#PART2    @MHIN
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN98
     C           K#CEPL    CHAINFCEPL01              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE *ON       EXIST2
     C                     ENDIF
      * --- Print Err Report CUSTOMER PART DOES NOT EXIST! -----
     C                     SELEC
     C           EXIST1    WHEQ *OFF
     C           EXIST2    ANDEQ*OFF
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,4     XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
      *
     C           EXIST1    WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVELB7NONY    @NONY
     C                     MOVELB7NKJO    @FACT
     C                     MOVELB7NUKE    @DOCK
     C                     MOVELB7SHN1    K@SHN1
     C                     MOVELB7SHN2    K@SHN2
     C                     MOVELB7SHN3    K@SHN3
      *
     C           EXIST2    WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVELA2BHB1    K@SHN1
     C                     MOVELA2BHB2    K@SHN2
     C                     MOVELA2BHB3    K@SHN3
     C                     ENDSL
      *
      * F: Check UNIT PRICE -----------------------------------
     C           #UP       IFEQ 0
      *     Print Err Report:
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,5     XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      * H: Check EFFECTIVE DATE  ------------------------------
     C                     MOVEL#EFDTX    @VLDAT
     C                     CALL 'UTLR01'
     C                     PARM           @VLDAT 10
     C                     PARM           #TRUE   8
     C                     PARM           #RTN    1
     C           #RTN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL#TRUE     #EFDT   80
     C                     ELSE
      *     Print Err Report: ERROR - EFFECTIVE DATE IS NOT IN CALENDAR..
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,2     XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * H: Check EFFECTIVE DATE 2------------------------------
     C           #RTN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C           #ERFLG    ANDEQ*OFF
     C                     MOVEL#PART2    @MHIN
     C                     MOVEL#TOKU     @CUST
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @DELV
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN1    @MHN1
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN2    @MHN2
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN3    @MHN3
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN4    @MHN4
     C                     CALL 'FBCR73'
     C                     PARM           @CUST   4
     C                     PARM           @DELV   4
     C                     PARM           @FACT   1
     C                     PARM           @DOCK   4
     C                     PARM           @MHN1   5
     C                     PARM           @MHN2   5
     C                     PARM           @MHN3   5
     C                     PARM           @MHN4   5
     C                     PARM           #EFDAT  8
     C                     PARM           #RTN2   1
JW1   **
 |   C**         #RTN2     IFEQ *BLANK
 |   C**         #TRUE     ANDLE#EFDAT
 |    **Print Error Report
 |   C**                   ADD  1         ER@CNT
 |   C**                   MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
 |   C**                   MOVELMSG,11    XMSG
 |   C**                   MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
 |   C**                   MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
 |   C**                   MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
 |   C**                   EXSR @PRINT
JW1  C**                   ENDIF
      **
     C                     ENDIF
      * I:Check EXPIRATION DATE --------------------
     C           #EXDTX    IFEQ '99999999'
     C                     MOVEL#EXDTX    #EXDT   80
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL#EXDTX    @VLDAT
     C                     CALL 'UTLR01'
     C                     PARM           @VLDAT 10
     C                     PARM           #TRUE   8
     C                     PARM           #RTN    1
     C           #RTN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL#TRUE     #EXDT
     C                     ELSE
      *     Print Err Report: ERROR - EXPIRATION DATE IS NOT IN CALENDAR..
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,10    XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      * *:Check EFFECTIVE DATE < EXPIRATION DATE ------------
     C           #EFDT     IFGT #EXDT
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,13    XMSG
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      * -------------------------------------------------
      * CHECK W/PRICE MASTER, IF DUPLICATE DATA
     C           #ERFLG    IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL#NONY     @NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     @FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     @DOCK
     C                     MOVEL#EFDT     @EFDT
     C           KEY03B    CHAINFBCPL03              96
     C           *IN96     IFEQ *OFF
     C           #UP       ANDEQFBNTAN
     C           #EFDT     ANDEQFBTKHZ
JW   C           #EXDT     ANDEQFBTSHZ
     C                     ADD  1         ER@CNT
     C                     MOVE *ON       #ERFLG
     C                     MOVELMSG,12    XMSG
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
      * ADD: WARNING
     C           *IN96     IFEQ *ON
     C                     ADD  1         WR@CNT
     C                     MOVELMSG,3     XMSG
     C                     EXSR @PRINT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * IF ERROR, SKIP --------------------------------
     C           #ERFLG    IFEQ *ON
     C                     GOTO @SKIP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * IF NO ERROR, WRITE FBCWP84 (WORK)--------------
     C                     ADD  1         OK@CNT
     C                     EXSR #WRT
      * ------------------------------------------
     C           @SKIP     TAG
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      ******************************************************
      *          WRITE FBCWP84
      ******************************************************
     C           #WRT      BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARFBCWP841
     C                     Z-ADDLIN#      F4LINE
     C                     Z-ADD#TOKU     F4TOKU
     C                     Z-ADD#NONY     F4NONY
     C                     MOVEL#FACT     F4FACT
     C                     MOVEL#DOCK     F4DOCK
     C                     Z-ADD#EFDT     F4EFDT
     C                     Z-ADD#EXDT     F4EXDT
     C                     MOVEL#PART2    @MHIN
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN1    F4MHN1
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN2    F4MHN2
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN3    F4MHN3
     C                     MOVEL@MHIN4    F4MHN4
     C                     MOVELK@SHN1    F4SHN1
     C                     MOVELK@SHN2    F4SHN2
     C                     MOVELK@SHN3    F4SHN3
     C                     Z-ADD#UP       F4UP1
     C                     Z-ADD@DATE     F4CDAT
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     F4CTIM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     F4USER
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      F4PGM
      *
     C                     WRITEFBCWP841
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      ******************************************************
      *          @GET: GET INPUT FIELDS
      ******************************************************
     C           @GET      BEGSR
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #TOKUX  4
     C                     Z-ADD0         #TOKU   40
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #NONYX  4
     C                     Z-ADD0         #NONY   40
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #FACT   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #DOCK   4
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #PART  20
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #UPX    6
     C                     Z-ADD0         #UP     65
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #EFDTX 10
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    #EXDTX 10
     C                     MOVE *OFF      #HDFLG  1        HEADER FLAG
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     IX      50
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     IY      50
      * A:GET CUSTOMER#--------------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#A     #TOKUX
     C                     Z-ADD0         #TOKU
     C           WKCKSU    CHECK#TOKUX                   99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
JW3  C                     MOVEL#TOKUX    $IN       P
 .   C                     CALL 'UTLR60'
 .   C                     PARM           $IN    17
 .   C                     PARM           $TRUE  156
 .   C                     PARM           $RTN    1
JW3  C                     Z-ADD$TRUE     NUM4
JW3  C                     MOVELNUM4      #TOKU
     C                     ENDIF
      *   IF CUST# FIELD IS NOT NUMERIC, THEN IT IS HEADER
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE *ON       #HDFLG
     C                     GOTO EGET
     C                     ENDIF
      * B:GET DELIVERY#--------------------------------
      * CONVERT LTR TO NUM
     C                     MOVELFLD#B     $IN
     C                     CALL 'UTLR60'
     C                     PARM           $IN    17
     C                     PARM           $TRUE  156
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
     C                     Z-ADD$TRUE     NUM4    40
      *
     C                     MOVELNUM4      #NONYX
     C                     Z-ADD0         #NONY
     C           WKCKSU    CHECK#NONYX                   99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL#NONYX    #NONY
     C                     ENDIF
      * C:GET FACTORY ---------------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#C     #FACT
      * D:GET DOCK    ---------------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#D     #DOCK
      * E:GET PART#   ---------------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#E     #PART
     C                     MOVELFLD#E     #PART2 20
      *       (1) Remove '-' from #PART and save to #PART2
     C**JW2                Z-ADD1         IX
     C**                   Z-ADD0         IY
     C**                   MOVEAFLD#E     MV1
     C**                   MOVEAFLD#E     MV2
     C**         '-'       LOKUPMV1,IX                   99
     C**         *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C**         IX        SUB  1         IY
     C**         1         DO   20
     C**                   ADD  1         IX
     C**                   ADD  1         IY
     C**         MV1,IX    IFEQ *BLANK
     C**                   MOVE MV1,IX    MV2,IY
     C**                   LEAVE
     C**                   ELSE
     C**                   MOVE MV1,IX    MV2,IY
     C**                   ENDIF
     C**                   ENDDO
     C**                   ENDIF
JW2  C                     MOVELFLD#E     $FLD1     P
 .   C                     CALL 'UUUR05'
 .   C                     PARM           $FLD1  25
 .   C                     PARM           $FLD2  25
JW2  C                     MOVEL$FLD2     #PART2
      * F:GET UNIT PRICE ------------------------------
     C                     Z-ADD0         IX
     C                     Z-ADD0         IY
     C                     MOVEL*ALL'0'   FLD
     C                     CLEARCSV
     C                     MOVELFLD#F     #UPX
     C                     MOVEAFLD#F     CSV
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     ADD  1         IX
     C           CSV,IX    IFEQ ' '
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C           CSV,IX    IFEQ '.'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C           CSV,IX    IFEQ '$'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ADD  1         IY
     C                     MOVELCSV,IX    FLD,IY
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEAFLD       W@FLD6
      * CHECK NUMERIC
     C           WKCKSU    CHECKW@FLD6                   99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     Z-ADDW@NUM6    #UP
     C                     ENDIF
      * H:GET EFFECTIVE DATE---------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#G     #EFDTX
      * I:GET EXPIRATION DATE--------------------------
     C                     MOVELFLD#H     LTR4    4
     C           LTR4      IFEQ '9999'
     C           LTR4      OREQ '9/99'
     C           LTR4      OREQ '99/9'
     C                     MOVEL'99999999'#EXDTX
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELFLD#H     #EXDTX
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           EGET      TAG
     C                     ENDSR
      ******************************************************
      *          @PRINT: PRINT ERROR REPORT
      ******************************************************
     C           @PRINT    BEGSR
      *
     C   OF                EXCPTHDR1
     C   OF                SETOF                     OF
     C                     ADD  1         SEQ
      *
     C                     EXCPTDTL1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      ******************************************************
      *                  INITIAL ROUTINE
      ******************************************************
     C           @INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           #STS    1
     C                     PARM           #MSG1  80
     C                     PARM           #MSG2  80
      *
     C           K#PART    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN1
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN2
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN3
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN4
     C                     KFLD           #TOKU
     C                     KFLD           #NONY
     C                     KFLD           #FACT
     C                     KFLD           #DOCK
      *
     C           K#CEPL    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN1
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN2
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN5
      *
     C           KEY03     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #TOKU
     C                     KFLD           @NONY
     C                     KFLD           @FACT
     C                     KFLD           @DOCK
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN1
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN2
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN3
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN4
     C                     KFLD           @TKYY
     C                     KFLD           @TKMM
     C                     KFLD           @TKDD
      *
     C           KEY03B    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #TOKU
     C                     KFLD           @NONY
     C                     KFLD           @FACT
     C                     KFLD           @DOCK
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN1
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN2
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN3
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN4
      *
     C           K#PL08    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN1
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN2
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN3
     C                     KFLD           @MHIN4
     C                     KFLD           K@TOKU  40
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     @DATE   80
     C                     TIME           @TIME   60
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INOF
     C                     MOVE *OFF      #STS
     C                     CLEAR#MSG1
     C                     CLEAR#MSG2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XMSG
     C                     Z-ADD0         SEQ     50
     C                     Z-ADD0         ER@CNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         WR@CNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         OK@CNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         NM@CNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         WR@CNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         DAT#    50
     C                     Z-ADD0         TTL#    50
     C                     Z-ADD0         LIN#    50
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLD3   20
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLD4   20
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @NONY   40
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @FACT   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @DOCK   4
     C                     MOVELMSG,1     @TITL  43
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *************************************************************
      *                    OUTPUT                                 *
      *************************************************************
     OQPRINT  E  102           HDR1
     O                                    8 'PROGRAM:'
     O                         #PGM      17
     O                         #USER     30
     O                         @TITL     80
     O                                  100 'DATE'
     O                         @DATE    111 '    .  .  '
     O                         @TIME    120 '  :  :  '
     O                         PAGE  Z  130
     O                                  126 'PAGE'
     O        E  1             HDR1
     O                                    4 'ERR'
     O                                   11 'LINE#'
     O                                   16 'CUST'
     O                                   21 'DELV'
     O                                   23 'F'
     O                                   29 'DOCK'
     O                                   39 'CUST_PART'
     O                                   62 'INTRAL PART'
     O                                   73 'U/PRICE'
     O                                   82 'EFFECTVE'
     O                                   93 'EXP_DATE'
     O                                  105 'ERROR MSG'
     O        E  1             HDR1
     O                                   20 '--------------------'
     O                                   40 '--------------------'
     O                                   60 '--------------------'
     O                                   80 '--------------------'
     O                                  100 '--------------------'
     O                                  120 '--------------------'
     O                                  130 '----------'
      *
     O        E  1             DTL1
     O                         SEQ   Z    5
     O                         LIN#  Z   11
     O                         #TOKU   +  1
     O                         @NONY   +  1
     O                         @FACT   +  1
     O                         @DOCK   +  1
     O                         #PART   +  2
     O                         K@SHN1  +  1
     O                         K@SHN2  +  1
     O                         K@SHN3  +  1
     O                         #UP   3 +  1
     O                         #EFDTX  +  1
     O                         #EXDTX  +  1
     O                         XMSG     132
      *
     O        E  1             FOT1
     O                                   20 '--------------------'
     O                                   40 '--------------------'
     O                                   60 '--------------------'
     O                                   80 '--------------------'
     O                                  100 '--------------------'
     O                                  120 '--------------------'
     O                                  130 '----------'
      *
     O        E  1             FOT1
     O                                   18 '** TOTAL RECORDS:'
     O                         DAT#  3   23
     O                                   31 ', ERROR:'
     O                         ER@CNT3   36
     O                                   46 ', WARNED: '
     O                         WR@CNT3   51
     O                                   56 ', OK:'
     O                         OK@CNT3   61
** (MSG) 1.........2.........3....+
 ** SALES UNIT PRICE UPLOAD ERROR REPORT **
ERR- EFFECTIVE DATE IS INVALID!
WRN- NEW CUS/DLV/F/DOCK CREATE!
ERR- COMMON PART OR IAF PART ERROR!
ERR- PRICE SHOULD NOT BE 0!
Error Does Not Exist. Total:xxxxx (Warning:xxxxx). Enter G:Update or C:Cancel.
Error Found! Error:xxxxx, Warning:xxxxx, OK:xxxxx. Enter G:Update or C:Cancel.
ERR- CUSTOMER# NOT FOUND!
ERR- DELIVERY# NOT FOUND!
ERR- EXPIRATION DATE IS INVALID!
ERR- EFFECTIVE DATE <= CURRENT!
ERR- DUPLICATE DATA FOUND!
ERR- EFFECTIVE DATE > EXP DATE!
